525
00:45:55,010 --> 00:45:57,880
I don’t care what that
immature diabolical brat said.

526
00:46:00,630 --> 00:46:01,230
What?

527
00:46:02,450 --> 00:46:03,210
I don’t care.

528
00:46:05,530 --> 00:46:08,170
