537
00:46:39,210 --> 00:46:40,630
Banging in the fitting room?

538
00:46:47,780 --> 00:46:48,970
I like a writer.

539
00:46:50,140 --> 00:46:53,600
That’s why... I have to be imaginative.

540
00:47:03,750 --> 00:47:04,580
